  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>basmati rice </strong>and 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[320ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1582891773891-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1582891773891-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1582891773891-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1582891773891-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1582891773891-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, drain and rinse your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p><p>Peel, finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1582891830499-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1582891830499-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1582891830499-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1582891830499-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1582891830499-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain your <strong>jumbo king prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan and cook for 6-7 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h19m42s-APIC-1653322987460-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h19m42s-APIC-1653322987460-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h19m42s-APIC-1653322987460-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h19m42s-APIC-1653322987460-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h19m42s-APIC-1653322987460-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Combine the juice<strong> </strong>of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lime[s]</strong> with your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> mayo </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>chipotle-lime mayo</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1582891793971-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1582891793971-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1582891793971-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1582891793971-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1582891793971-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove the <strong>outer lettuce leaves</strong> and set aside, then shred the <strong>inner core[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1582891797764-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1582891797764-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1582891797764-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1582891797764-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1582891797764-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are almost cooked, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano </strong>and cook for 1 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h31m55s-APIC-1653322996606-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h31m55s-APIC-1653322996606-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h31m55s-APIC-1653322996606-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h31m55s-APIC-1653322996606-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-04-22_11h31m55s-APIC-1653322996606-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>basmati rice</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Remove the pan from the heat, then add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>,<strong> chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> and<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy Mexican-style jumbo prawn rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1582891804788-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1582891804788-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1582891804788-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1582891804788-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1582891804788-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy Mexican-style jumbo prawn rice</strong> with a<strong> lime wedge</strong> and <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>chipotle-lime mayo</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
